{"tid":1761152,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"如果寫個夾單網/APP有無人想用？","createTime":"2019-11-28T17:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T12:18:29.000Z","uid":184103,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"87d85c55855bc3f34113b5aee85ea9d69bd32f3d","tid":1761152,"uid":184103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T17:02:36.000Z","msg":"最近black friday想買野 但搵唔到人夾 <br />\n所以有呢的構思<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有咩功能？<br />\n任何人都可以申請會員<br />\n申請完可以開post 話想去邊個網買野<br />\n目標夾幾多錢 有咩優惠 deadline<br />\n任何會員都可以下面留低想買啲咩<br />\n全部人都會睇到其他人留言<br />\n但只有開post個人可以睇到留言者聯絡方式<br />\n點樣交收就開post個人自己統籌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ: 收費?<br />\n應該唔會收費<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAWS有免費一年host <br />\n咁應該可以玩到最少一年<br />\n之後如果有贊助呢啲就繼續搞<br />\n無就收皮<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有咩目的?<br />\n其實主要係想整個portfolio方便搵工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf3235dfb5258da13eb485cbb9f9b85d808eaec","tid":1761152,"uid":137871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"輕輕推"},{"pid":"c80d1d5226f01b7f672393bae9a7cd89e415bd07","tid":1761152,"uid":309357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T17:05:58.000Z","msg":"講下個流程運作，好似幾得意"},{"pid":"8f7ee8abd71daae7746ef09739671d544ff60c2c","tid":1761152,"uid":37193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T17:06:30.000Z","msg":"聽落又幾有計"},{"pid":"af5bbb6c0fe0cf29a6171cdc4d7c954c05364bb3","tid":1761152,"uid":89873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T17:09:12.000Z","msg":"咪即係團購囉<br />\n不過係反向咋嘛<br />\n而家咁樣更複雜"},{"pid":"ad4e84d60760b0477d23a57c2902681187801657","tid":1761152,"uid":184103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c80d1d5226f01b7f672393bae9a7cd89e415bd07","tid":1761152,"uid":309357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T17:05:58.000Z","msg":"講下個流程運作，好似幾得意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T00:15:17.000Z","msg":"即係好似ASOS買滿$5